{
  "stem": "5430.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember once my sister and I went to see a Jewish show, [NON-ENGLISH], 'We're Going to America.' It was a comedy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I still remember scenes from it, the, the traveling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Jewish stage was very strong, and my father [INAUDIBLE] was a friend of Ida Kaminska, which is the-- who was the star of the Jewish theater in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, the Jewish movies were very strong and prevalent and made in Warsaw also.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, one of my uncles-- my father's brother--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Israel, Israel Bornstein, had a bit part in the movie And I'm still trying to find a copy of this movie.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow, all the Jewish movies have been reproduced in videos except that one, Because I know he was-- had a part in it, like davening before the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a tall man with a long beard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would have liked to get a strip of it, a piece of--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody went to see.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the [INAUDIBLE], he, he was the star of the family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody else was in the movies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was just a bit picture, you know, a bit part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- well, I could say the theater mostly was in the-- in the so-called Jewish section of Warsaw, which is later became the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I would say a half a dozen blocks in all-- Zamenhof, [POLISH], you know, the-- all the-- which are no longer there, by the way, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You mean as far--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In '39?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I remember the war, sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this is-- things start-- when things started changing in Warsaw itself, we were already-- we had left.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- we kept--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Do you remember when you heard about the invasion?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
